<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="later-adv">later <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'leɪtə(r)/    美 /'leɪtər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>以后；后来：</strong></h4>
<p>反 earlier </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>See you later.  
再见。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>About fifteen minutes later, the rain stopped. 
大约15分钟后，雨停了。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 5</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Eating breakfast keeps you from overeating later in the day.  
吃早餐可防止你一天其他时间过量饮食。</p><footer>2009 全国</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="later-on">later on</h3>
<p>1.<strong>以后；过后：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Later on he realized his mistake. 
后来他认识到了自己的错误。</p></div></div>